      "content": "yo u ever notice how search autocompletes have been acting super weird lately?? like i was typing stuff about my neighborhood and it kept suggesting phrases that made zero sense unless u knew something specific about my daily routine. it feels like its not just an algorithm anymore. like something is actually watching and trying to talk to me through the suggestions. u think that's even possible?",
